│ stop({"edit_points": [[158, 159, "llvm/lib/Transforms/Utils/LCSSA.cpp"]], "thoughts": "### │
│ 1. Understanding the Issue\nThe issue lies in the `formLCSSAForInstructionsImpl` function, │
│ specifically in the logic that determines whether a `DomBB` dominates an `ExitBB`. The     │
│ transformation assumes that `DomBB` dominates `ExitBB` without properly handling cases     │
